parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: The client token that is used to ensure the idempotence of the request. You can use the client to generate the value that is unique among different requests. The `ClientToken` value can only contain ASCII characters and cannot exceed 64 characters in length. For more information, see [How to ensure idempotence](~~25693~~).

parameters.name: Reason
parameters.description: The reason for deleting the filing form. Enter details.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the filed instance. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
